Recipe for hawaii pizza. Caro Nonno Pizzeria will remain neutral in the discussion about pineapple on a pizza. Note: this is a vegetarian recipe so it doesn't contain ham.

Ingredients
- pizza dough
- tomato sauce
- pineapple
- pesto
- parmesan cheese
- poblano peppers

Directions
- Preheat the oven to 180 degrees C
- Put the sauce on your pizza dough
- Distribute the pineapple, pesto and cheese over the pizza evely
- Put the pizza in the oven for about 12 minutes (depending on your oven)
- Enjoy!

